    "English": "A sealed bottle, found floating in the water. There appears to be a message from <span class=\"name name-stellar\">the Angler</span> inside.<br><br>Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to <span class=\"name name-stellar\">unseal</span> the bottle and read the message within.",
